  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1135881">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1135881/" class="title-link">美不胜收的古文字</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1135881"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tigerthrash/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1123571-31.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tigerthrash/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">吕蕤冰</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-03-19"
      class="main-meta">2007-03-19 20:55:31</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1135881_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  既为趣谈，确实妙趣横生，美不胜收。汉字活了，灵动起来，好像天天和你生活在一起的黄脸婆，本来你看见她都不会再有什么想法，一天忽然打扮了下，竟让你有了初恋时的冲动。  而创造了这些字的古人们，他们的生活、兴趣、喜怒，竟然也好像从小长大的筒子楼里邻居，笑骂都在眼前了。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1135881_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1135881_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5482173">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5482173/" class="title-link">关于假借字的几点想法</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5482173"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1964687/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1964687-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1964687/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">石头</span>
